sentences.english: The contract contains options for additional payloads that would add to the initial award value.
sentences.chinese: 合同包含了可能会添加到最初授予价值的额外的载荷。

sentences.english: High contact angles carry high axial loads.
sentences.chinese: 高接触角带有相当的轴向载荷。

sentences.english: The results of the analysis is a reference for wind turbine blade loads research.
sentences.chinese: 分析结果可为风力机叶片载荷研究做参考。

sentences.english: Conclusion The thickness of porcelain laminate veneers has less effect on the stress distribution.
sentences.chinese: 结论瓷贴面厚度对其载荷后应力分布影响较小。

sentences.english: A helicopter mathematical model with a slung load is described.
sentences.chinese: 建立带吊挂载荷的直升机飞行动力学模型。

sentences.english: Current has obviously affected on wear rate compared with loading.
sentences.chinese: 在试验范围内，电流比载荷对磨损率的影响显著。

sentences.english: Loads distort every component of the structure of the Cassegrain antenna system.
sentences.chinese: 载荷使卡塞格伦天线结构的每个部分发生变形。

sentences.english: Carried out a large number of force tests of single-row tooth systematically.
sentences.chinese: 系统地开展了大量的单齿圈牙齿载荷测试实验。

sentences.english: The path of crack initiation and growth is transgranular under conditions of isothermal low cycle fatigue.
sentences.chinese: 在等温低周疲劳载荷下，裂纹主要为穿晶萌生与扩展。

sentences.english: The deformations (deflection value) of the patterns with different coatings were measured under different loads.
sentences.chinese: 测试涂挂不同涂料的模样在变载荷下的挠度值。

sentences.english: Message payload and message meta data.
sentences.chinese: 消息有效载荷与消息元数据。

sentences.english: Additional payloads will be integrated into the air vehicle and control segment in the future.
sentences.chinese: 未来，还会有其他载荷被集成到无人机和控制部分中。

sentences.english: Some important issues such as the increase of the load of the nose landing-gear are analyzed.
sentences.chinese: 文章中还分析了分级甲板会增大前起落架载荷等问题。

sentences.english: All lifting appliances must be clearly marked with an identification number and with their safe working loads.
sentences.chinese: 所有起重器具必须清楚标明标识号和其安全作业载荷。

sentences.english: The correction rapid-loading test is a new method of loading test for composite foundation.
sentences.chinese: 修正快压法是复合地基载荷试验的新方法。

sentences.english: Delaminations may reduce the buckling load of the laminated structure greatly.
sentences.chinese: 脱层的存在将会大大降低层合结构的屈曲载荷。
